----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
You decide to leave your room and seek help. Curiosity drives you towards your sister's room,
where strange noises echo through the air. As you enter, you find chaos, with flipped furniture
and scattered belongings.As you look around the room, a flickering mirror catches your eye, drawing 
you closer. Without hesitation, you touch it, and the mirror instantly breaks making you terrified
for what lays ahead. Determined to uncover the truth and protect your family,you take on a courageous 
journey through this terrifying experience.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
